<div>
<p>DJV Imaging provides open source movie playback software for use in film
production, VFX, and computer animation. Key features include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Real-time playback of image sequences and movies</li>
    <li>Support for industry standard file formats including Cineon, DPX,
        OpenEXR, and QuickTime</li>
    <li>Command line utilities for batch processing</li>
    <li>Cross platform support for Linux, Apple OS X, and Microsoft Windows</li>
</ul>
</div>

